If you could please inform me how to send photos by internet to the Hearn Residence, I would appreciate it.
Also, I have one  published rarity:   GOMBO ZHEBES Little Dictionary of Creole Proverbs, published in New York in 1885.   My copy came from the Long Island Historical Society, when they deaccessed many books and artworks.
