<CENTER><H2>Lafacdio Hearn in <BR> <I>Atlantic Monthly, Harper's Monthly, The Century</I></H2>
online at Cornell University's <A HREF="http://cdl.library.cornell.edu/moa/">Making of America website</A><BR><FONT SIZE=-1>(From <I>The Atlantic</I> if not otherwise marked)</FONT></CENTER>
<OL>
<LI><A HREF="http://cdl.library.cornell.edu/cgi-bin/moa/moa-cgi?notisid=ABK2934-0078-28">About Faces in Japanese Art</A>,<FONT SIZE=-1> August 1896, Volume 78, Issue 466, pp. 219-227</FONT>

