<HR><FONT SIZE=-1>
Photograph by Frederick Gutekunst, 1889: Lafcadio Hearn, age thirty-nine, shortly before his departure for Japan.  <I>Lafcadio Hearn Collection, Rare Books Section, Howard-Tilton Memorial Library, Tulane University.
<P><I>The title characters are the Japanese characters for Koizumi Yakumo, Hearn's Japanese name: ko-izumi 'small spring,' ya-kumo 'eight clouds'.</I></FONT>

